in","created_on":"2026-04-02T16:17:00Z"},{"id":14476,"profile_image":"https://thespacedevs-prod.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/profile_images/cosmic2520penguin_profile_20210817212020.png","comment":"Delayed to NET April 4 per NOTAMs, to be confirmed.","info_url":"https://forum.nasaspaceflight.com/index.php?topic=64450.msg2773264#msg2773264","created_by":"Cosmic_Penguin","created_on":"2026-03-28T22:32:00Z"},{"id":14473,"profile_image":"https://thespacedevs-prod.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/profile_images/cosmic2520penguin_profile_20210817212020.png","comment":"Delayed due to launch site weather, new launch date TBD.","info_url":"https://x.com/ulalaunch/status/2037911210490798243","created_by":"Cosmic_Penguin","created_on":"2026-03-28T15:36:00Z"},{"id":14465,"profile_image":"https://thespacedevs-prod.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/profile_images/cosmic2520penguin_profile_20210817212020.png","comment":"Updated launch weather, 10% GO.","info_url":"https://www.24live.co/live/UIspI?n=4075120816102317368","created_by":"Cosmic_Penguin","created_on":"2026-03-27T20:24:00Z"},{"id":14447,"profile_image":"https://thespacedevs-prod.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/profile_images/cosmic2520penguin_profile_20210817212020.png","comment":"Updated launch weather, 20% GO.","info_url":"https://www.24live.co/live/UIspI?n=4074322020309389656","created_by":"Cosmic_Penguin","created_on":"2026-03-26T13:46:00Z"},{"id":14352,"profile_image":"https://thespacedevs-prod.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/profile_images/cosmic2520penguin_profile_20210817212020.png","comment":"Moved up to March 29.","info_url":"https://x.com/ulalaunch/status/2034284281590120612","created_by":"Cosmic_Penguin","created_on":"2026-03-18T15:06:00Z"},{"id":14243,"profile_image":"https://thespacedevs-prod.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/profile_images/cosmic2520penguin_profile_20210817212020.png","comment":"Added launch time.","info_url":"https://www.ulalaunch.com/missions/next-launch/atlas-v-amazon-leo-5","created_by":"Cosmic_Penguin","created_on":"2026-03-12T00:37:00Z"},{"id":14235,"profile_image":"https://thespacedevs-prod.nyc3.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/profile_images/cosmic2520penguin_profile_20210817212020.png","comment":"NET March 30.","info_url":"https://x.com/ulalaunch/status/2031747757950533674","created_by":"Cosmic_Penguin","created_on":"2026-03-11T15:05:00Z"}],"info_urls":[{"priority":10,"source":"ulalaunch.com","title":"Atlas V Amazon Leo 5","description":"ULA's Atlas V rocket will deliver another batch of satellites into low Earth orbit for Amazon Leo, the broadband constellation. Its mission is to provide fast, reliable internet to customers around the world, including those in unserved and underserved communities, using a network of more than 3,000...","feature_image":null,"url":"https://www.ulalaunch.com/missions/next-launch/atlas-v-amazon-leo-5","type":{"id":1,"name":"Official Page"},"language":{"id":1,"name":"English","code":"en"}}],"vid_urls":[{"priority":10,"source":null,"publisher":"United Launch Alliance","title":"Rocket Launch: Amazon Leo 5","description":"ULA's Atlas V rocket will deliver another batch of satellites into low Earth orbit for Amazon Leo, the broadband constellation. Amazon Leo's mission is to provide fast, reliable internet to customers around the world, including those in unserved and underserved communities, using a network of more than 3,000 LEO satellites.  \n\nGO Atlas! GO Centaur! GO Leo 5!","feature_image":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/NAKuVmkp5q8/maxresdefault.jpg","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NAKuVmkp5q8","type":{"id":1,"name":"Official Webcast"},"language":{"id":1,"name":"English","code":"en"},"start_time":"2026-04-04T05:25:31Z","end_time":"2026-04-04T06:25:10Z","live":false},{"priority":11,"source":"youtube.com","publisher":"Spaceflight Now","title":"Watch live: ULA Atlas 5 rocket launches 29 Amazon Leo satellites from Cape Canaveral","description":"Watch live coverage of the launch of a United Launch Alliance Atlas 5 rocket with a batch of 29 satellites for Amazon's Leo internet service on Saturday, April 4, 2026. Liftoff is scheduled during  a 29-minute launch window that opens at 1:45 a.m. EDT (0545 UTC). The rocket will take a north-easterly trajectory on departure from Florida's Space Coast.\n\nAmazon’s LEO satellite internet constellation, originally called Project Kuiper, is designed to rival others, like SpaceX’s Starlink and Eutelsat's OneWeb.\n\nThe mission features the most powerful Atlas 5 configuration, the 551, equipped with five solid rocket boosters from Northrop Grumman.\n\nCommentary will be provided by Spaceflight Now's Will Robinson-Smith, starting approximately one hour prior to liftoff.\n\nVideos like this are made ...","feature_image":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7b01rQjEFl4/maxresdefault.jpg","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7b01rQjEFl4","type":{"id":3,"name":"Unofficial Webcast"},"language":{"id":1,"name":"English","code":"en"},"start_time":"2026-04-04T04:46:10Z","end_time":"2026-04-04T06:30:42Z","live":false},{"priority":12,"source":"youtube.com","publisher":"NASASpaceflight","title":"ULA Atlas V 551 launches Amazon Leo Atlas 5 (LA-05)","description":"ULA Atlas V launch of the Amazon Leo Atlas 5 (LA-05) mission from SLC-41.\n\nLaunch Window: April 4th from 1:45AM to 2:14AM EDT (05:45-06:14 UTC)\nCurrent T0: April 4th at 1:45AM EDT (05:45 UTC)\n\nMission: Atlas V 551 launch of a batch of 29 Amazon Leo satellites into orbit.\nLaunch location: Space Launch Complex 41 (SLC-41), Cape Canaveral Space Force Station, Earth. \nTarget orbit: Low-Earth Orbit (LEO); ~450km circular orbit at 51.9º inclination\nBooster: AV-109\nConfiguration: 551\n  - 5 meter wide, medium length version payload fairing\n  - 5 GEM 63 solid rocket motors\n  - 1 RL10C-1-1 engine on Centaur\n  - Nicknamed \"Bruiser\"\nRocket trajectory: Northeast flying parallel to the US east coast.\nPayload mass: ~16540kg (~36500lbs)\nStats:\n  - ULA's 171st launch overall and its 2nd of the year.\n ...","feature_image":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/6SiX9UPKq8Y/maxresdefault.jpg","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6SiX9UPKq8Y","type":{"id":3,"name":"Unofficial Webcast"},"language":{"id":1,"name":"English","code":"en"},"start_time":"2026-04-04T04:47:33Z","end_time":"2026-04-04T06:32:22Z","live":false}],"timeline":[],"pad_turnaround":"P50DT20H24M","mission_patches":[]}